<P>
The City Council appointed 10 people to serve on two new advisory panels: the 
Recreation and Parks Commission and the Public Works Commission. 
</P>
<P>
The commissioners will assist in planning issues for the city's parks and 
public projects. 
</P>
<P>
Named to the parks commission were Ellen Stern Harris, John Melnick, Stephen 
Kravit, Rudy Cole and Lona Stone. The new public works panel members are Mark 
Egerman, Betty Harris, Ron Cooper, Robert Silberman and Gloria Seiff. 
</P>
<P>
The commission members will serve four-year terms. 
</P>
